{"content": "I need to multiply 620\u2089 \u00d7 872\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n620\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 2\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 2\u00d79 + 0\u00d71 = 486 + 18 + 0 = 504\u2081\u2080\n\n872\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 2\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 2\u00d71 = 648 + 63 + 2 = 713\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n504 \u00d7 713 = 359,352\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n359352 \u00f7 9 = 39928 r 0\n39928 \u00f7 9 = 4436 r 4\n4436 \u00f7 9 = 492 r 8\n492 \u00f7 9 = 54 r 6\n54 \u00f7 9 = 6 r 0\n6 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 6\n\nReading from bottom to top: 606840\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n606840\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u2075 + 0\u00d79\u2074 + 6\u00d79\u00b3 + 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 4\u00d79\u00b9 + 0\u00d79\u2070\n= 6\u00d759049 + 0\u00d76561 + 6\u00d7729 + 8\u00d781 + 4\u00d79 + 0\u00d71\n= 354294 + 0 + 4374 + 648 + 36 + 0\n= 359352\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n606840", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 463}